## 4. Typography | الخطوط

### Arabic (Primary — RTL)
- **Display / H1:** IBM Plex Arabic — Bold (700)
- **Body / Labels:** IBM Plex Arabic — Regular (400) / Medium (500)
- **Technical Data:** Noto Sans Arabic — fits dense data tables (SKU, specs)

### Latin (Secondary — for technical terms, API routes, code)
- **Display:** Playfair Display — Bold/Italic (for marketing headers)
- **UI / Data:** Inter — Medium/Regular (for tables, forms, data)
- **Code / SKU:** JetBrains Mono — for SKU codes, API paths, technical values

